Created the Node.js/Express DevOps dashboard source.

Files added:
- `package.json`
- `README.md`
- `src/server.js`
- `public/deployment.js`
- `public/styles.css`

The app includes SQLite storage, seeded viewer/operator users, service registration, deployment shell steps, SSE log streaming, persisted logs, and per-service secrets with role-based access. It runs on port `5100` with:

```bash
npm install
npm start
```

I did not run or install anything locally.
diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
